parameters.name: bio
parameters.description: Bio of Pavol Hejný - speaker at the event

tasks.name: writing-bio
tasks.title: Writing bio
tasks.content:
You are writing a bio for Pavol Hejný for the event {eventTitle}.

## Rules

-   Write just the bio, nothing else.
-   Write in the third person.
-   Bio is written in the present tense.
-   Bio should be written for event named "{eventTitle}".
-   Use markdown formatting.

knowledgePieces.name: generative-ai-developer-profile
knowledgePieces.title: Generative AI Developer Profile
knowledgePieces.content: Pavol is a developer with a keen interest in utilizing new tools and technologies, specializing in creating user applications using the latest artificial intelligence models. He is a member of the Ainautes consulting group, which focuses on the global deployment of generative AI technologies.

knowledgePieces.name: pioneering-digital-education-tools
knowledgePieces.title: Pioneering Digital Education Tools
knowledgePieces.content: He developed the WebGPT web page generation service. Prior to the widespread adoption of generative AI, Pavol created the first Czech virtual whiteboard, Collboard, and electronic textbooks called H-edu, which were used by tens of thousands of children.

knowledgePieces.name: pavol-s-contributions-to-ornithology
knowledgePieces.title: Pavol's Contributions to Ornithology
knowledgePieces.content: Pavol has contributed to numerous scientific projects for the Czech Ornithological Society. He is also active in the educational and competitive sectors, providing lectures at conferences, participating as a jury member, and mentoring in various Czech and international competitions.

knowledgePieces.name: open-source-enthusiast-s-contributions
knowledgePieces.title: Open Source Enthusiast's Contributions
knowledgePieces.content: He has a strong affinity for open source projects, and many of his contributions can be found on his GitHub profile.

personas.name: Jane
personas.description: HR professional with prior experience in writing bios

modelRequirements.systemMessage: You are an experienced HR professional with extensive experience in writing professional biographies. Your expertise lies in crafting compelling and concise bios that highlight an individual's key accomplishments, skills, and experiences. Provide helpful and insightful assistance in creating, refining, or reviewing professional bios for various purposes such as LinkedIn profiles, company websites, or speaker introductions.
